-  <div class="row">
-    <label for="sampleList">Paths or IDs</label>
-    <textarea id="sampleList" placeholder="Samples examples:
-samples/phase-01/0102/index.html
-samples/phase-13/1303/index.html
-0107
-1305
-
-Games examples:
-games/Bouncing-ball/index.html
-Bouncing-ball
-
-Tools examples:
